snippet.title: Gigi Hadid Reveals Yolanda Tries To Prevent Zayn Malik To See His Daughter
snippet.description:
Gigi Hadid Reveals Yolanda Tries To Prevent Zayn Malik To See His Daughter 
after six years of dating it looks like the couple might be done for good this time. According to People, the couple has ended their relationship after several sources claim Zayn ‘struck’ Gigi’s mother, Yolanda Hadid during an argument that involved the two. Details of what exactly transpired between Yolanda and her grand-daughter’s father have been trickling out one after the other and it is safe to say these two don’t see eye to eye at all.
